  "description": "The MikroTik MTP250-53V47-OD is a robust outdoor AC/DC power supply built for high-demand network setups in the MikroTik netPower series. It delivers a 53V DC output with 250W total power, providing consistent and efficient energy to multiple connected devices. Housed in a durable IP67-rated enclosure, it offers excellent resistance to dust, humidity, and extreme temperatures, ensuring reliable performance in outdoor and industrial environments. This power supply is ideal for systems that require higher voltage, such as networks with PTZ security cameras, PoE switches, or other high-power MikroTik equipment. Designed for reliability, the MTP250-53V47-OD operates smoothly in a wide temperature range from -40°C to +70°C, making it suitable for various climates. With CE, EAC, and RoHS certifications, it guarantees safety and quality compliance. The MTP250-53V47-OD is a practical and long-lasting solution for stable, weather-resistant power delivery in professional network installations.",
